description:
base36 in python
================

yet another implementation for the positional numeral system using 36 as the radix.


installation
------------

::

    pip install base36


usage
-----

::

    import base36

    assert base36.dumps(19930503) == 'bv6h3'
    assert base36.loads('bv6h3') == 19930503
